name: Metabolic
public_notice: Metabolic has recently migrated from their old contract to a new one. For more information, please visit this post.
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en: Metabolic is creating an ecosystem with function in the Metaverse. Their main focus is a 3D virtual reality NFT game focused on building value in their playable evolutionary NFTs. They will also release swap and staking, proprietary wallet, NFTs, branded visa, and more that integrates into the function of the NFTs.
